ANGER
Anger will control who you are and it will not make you think straight
It will cloud your judgement and emotions
It will ruin your life and it will hurt the ones close to you
It will destroy what you have taken time to built and it will cause you grief
ANGER IS A POWERFUL THING THAT ONE MUST KNOW HOW TO RELEASE IT WITHOUT HURTING OTHERS BUT THEMSELVES.
It will cause frustrations and hatred between people that you are close to including your friends
So one must know how to release it through exercise and meditations
Then one can control their anger without getting frustrated

